moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家用乜?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHybrid apps嚟講, 大路嘅可以揀Ionic(<a href=\"https://ionicframework.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fionicframework.com%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e3ef6d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ionicframework.com/</a>), 小眾啲嘅試下Ratchet(<a href=\"http://goratchet.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoratchet.com%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2d390b86\" target=\"_blank\">http://goratchet.com/</a>)囉!</blockquote><br />\n我屌，上年先學完jquery, 咁快就收皮...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\njQuery呢個library都仲可以用呢做prototyping嘅, 但jQuery Mobile呢個framework出名多bugs, 就真係可免則免喇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今時今日我都贊成用jQuery, 原因係好似safari同ie依類唔跟Standard, 最好有lib可以common曬d野，反正都唔會慢得幾多，除非你要細同快先要pure js"},{"pid":"2789604f6ce3a012945e806e2760a7c90108310f","tid":144433,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>jQuery Mobile呢個framework好似已經完成歷史任務, 入咗博物館, RIP了!<br />\n<br />\n樓主想挖番佢條屍出嚟?! 何必呢, 畀佢安息吧! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家用乜?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHybrid apps嚟講, 大路嘅可以揀Ionic(<a href=\"https://ionicframework.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fionicframework.com%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e3ef6d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ionicframework.com/</a>), 小眾啲嘅試下Ratchet(<a href=\"http://goratchet.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoratchet.com%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2d390b86\" target=\"_blank\">http://goratchet.com/</a>)囉!</blockquote><br />\n我屌，上年先學完jquery, 咁快就收皮...</blockquote><br />\n其實jquery仲係好有用。。。 不過code呢家嘢日新月異，幾乎個月都要學唔同嘅library/api， depend你做咩喇，學晒係無可能/無意義。 jquery講到底都係js，js以前係無咩作為，不過至從nodejs之後未來幾年都應該係js稱霸，而且目前嚟計9成website front end都係用jquery，所以同學仔你唔駛咁灰喎。。。 問題係你要知道jquery同jquery mobile係兩個plugin，後者depend on前者and已經收皮，所以唔好為左佢啲垃圾mobile first概念用佢。要係mobile上做animation我推薦gsap，再上一層就pixijs，backend就你用到先再講喇"},{"pid":"a00c7e2df9599de1159bd163e2f99abaa4276f65","tid":144433,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>jQuery Mobile呢個framework好似已經完成歷史任務, 入咗博物館, RIP了!<br />\n<br />\n樓主想挖番佢條屍出嚟?! 何必呢, 畀佢安息吧! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家用乜?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHybrid apps嚟講, 大路嘅可以揀Ionic(<a href=\"https://ionicframework.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fionicframework.com%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e3ef6d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ionicframework.com/</a>), 小眾啲嘅試下Ratchet(<a href=\"http://goratchet.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoratchet.com%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2d390b86\" target=\"_blank\">http://goratchet.com/</a>)囉!</blockquote><br />\n我屌，上年先學完jquery, 咁快就收皮...</blockquote><br />\n其實jquery仲係好有用。。。 不過code呢家嘢日新月異，幾乎個月都要學唔同嘅library/api， depend你做咩喇，學晒係無可能/無意義。 jquery講到底都係js，js以前係無咩作為，不過至從nodejs之後未來幾年都應該係js稱霸，而且目前嚟計9成website front end都係用jquery，所以同學仔你唔駛咁灰喎。。。 問題係你要知道jquery同jquery mobile係兩個plugin，後者depend on前者and已經收皮，所以唔好為左佢啲垃圾mobile first概念用佢。要係mobile上做animation我推薦gsap，再上一層就pixijs，backend就你用到先再講喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082ec4a710ec3c42d3d6cacc930d8d5df7af0c37","tid":144433,"uid":69481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"感覺學左jQuery 有啲基本概念<br />\n再學返純javascript 比較容易, 可以根據jQuery啲function google"},{"pid":"eecf99d441319710f10b5e29aa162d80b8a62efe","tid":144433,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感覺學左jQuery 有啲基本概念<br />\n再學返純javascript 比較容易, 可以根據jQuery啲function google</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就掉轉嚟(i.e.先難後易), 先學咗用Vanilla JS舞咗DOM同AJAX一輪, 覺得比較麻煩, 其後轉用jQuery舞同樣嘅嘢發覺容易咗好多, 爽快好多!<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 平時如果要喺啲網站(e.g.lihkg, google)度做下簡單改動(i.e.當做實驗), 我會先用個<strong>bookmarklet</strong>嚟inject個jQuery library入去: <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">javascript:(function(e,s){e.src=s;e.onload=function(){jQuery.noConflict();console.log('jQuery%20injected');$=jQuery;};document.head.appendChild(e);})(document.createElement('script'),'<a href=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.slim.min.js'\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.jquery.com%2Fjquery-3.1.1.slim.min.js%27&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=80a981c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.slim.min.js'</a>)</span><br />\n<br />\n然係開個web console(按F12)嚟直接打啲jQuery code, 方便過你用Vanilla JS嚟改嘢!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(P.S. <strong>bookmarklet</strong>好似個個browser都用到, 我就bookmark咗上面條bookmarklet喺Firefox度用.)"},{"pid":"68dcacca350a0af8f5aa0ad93b77ec381d4a2ffd","tid":144433,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>感覺學左jQuery 有啲基本概念<br />\n再學返純javascript 比較容易, 可以根據jQuery啲function google</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就掉轉嚟(i.e.先難後易), 先學咗用Vanilla JS舞咗DOM同AJAX一輪, 覺得比較麻煩, 其後轉用jQuery舞同樣嘅嘢發覺容易咗好多, 爽快好多!<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 平時如果要喺啲網站(e.g.lihkg, google)度做下簡單改動(i.e.當做實驗), 我會先用個<strong>bookmarklet</strong>嚟inject個jQuery library入去: <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">javascript:(function(e,s){e.src=s;e.onload=function(){jQuery.noConflict();console.log('jQuery%20injected');$=jQuery;};document.head.appendChild(e);})(document.createElement('script'),'<a href=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.slim.min.js'\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.jquery.com%2Fjquery-3.1.1.slim.min.js%27&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=80a981c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.slim.min.js'</a>)</span><br />\n<br />\n然係開個web console(按F12)嚟直接打啲jQuery code, 方便過你用Vanilla JS嚟改嘢!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(P.S. <strong>bookmarklet</strong>好似個個browser都用到, 我就bookmark咗上面條bookmarklet喺Firefox度用.)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFor example (change this post's title from &quot;jquery mobile&quot; to &quot;jQuery Mobile is DEAD!&quot;) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/015908_3f3294a481124a62ac7ae9fd512327ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F015908_3f3294a481124a62ac7ae9fd512327ec.jpg&h=6c0396db&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}